Package: migrate
Type: Package
Title: Create Credit State Migration (Transition) Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ketchbrook Analytics
Maintainer: mthomas@ketchbrookanalytics.com
Description: Tools to help convert credit risk data at two time points 
    into traditional credit state migration (aka, "transition") matrices.
    At a higher level, 'migrate' is intended to help an analyst understand 
    how risk moved in their credit portfolio over a time inverval.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 1.0.2),
    tidyr (>= 1.1.0),
    emo (>= 0.0.0.9000),
    crayon (>= 1.3.4)
